      </style></div><div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center lg:mt-28 mb-12"><div class="flex justify-center md:justify-start"><img src="/car-images/buick-hero.jpg" alt="Used Buick auto parts hero image" class="w-full max-w-md rounded-2xl shadow-xl"/></div><div class="flex flex-col justify-center"><h3 class="font-semibold text-xl md:text-2xl mb-3 text-white">Used Buick Parts for Sale</h3><p class="text-[18px] leading-[30px] text-[#cecece]">Smart. Affordable. Reliable. That’s PartsCentral. Driving a Buick says something subtle but strong. You appreciate comfort that lasts, elegance without excess, and smooth performance that doesn’t need noise to be noticed. That’s why we provide used Buick parts that let you keep your car running like it was built to. Every part is OEM, tested, and shipped nationwide at prices you can trust.</p></div></div><div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto space-y-14"><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Smart. Affordable. Reliable. That’s PartsCentral.</h3><ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2 text-[#cecece]"><li>OEM used Buick parts tested for performance and reliability</li><li>Nationwide shipping at prices you can trust</li><li>Designed to preserve comfort, elegance, and smooth performance</li><li>Built to keep your Buick running the way it was meant to</li></ul></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Buick Isn’t Just a Car. It’s a Mindset</h3><p class="text-[20px] text-[#cecece] leading-[34px] mb-3">A Buick is for those who don’t chase trends. It’s for people who believe in quiet confidence, timeless comfort, and the kind of ride that makes every trip feel deliberate. You don’t just drive a Buick. You drive with purpose. And with our Buick auto parts, you can preserve that unique driving experience — part by part.</p></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Popular Buick Auto Parts We Carry</h3><ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2 text-[#cecece]"><li>Engines and transmissions</li><li>Window regulators and motors</li><li>Starters, alternators, wiring</li><li>AC compressors and condensers</li><li>Doors, bumpers, mirrors</li><li>Radiators, fans, hoses</li><li>Suspension and steering components</li><li>Control arms, knuckles, axles</li><li>Headlights, taillights, switches</li></ul></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Built to Last. Backed by Us</h3><p class="text-[20px] text-[#cecece] leading-[34px] mb-3">Every part we sell is thoroughly inspected for performance, safety, and fitment. If we wouldn’t put it in our own Buick, we won’t list it. Because when you value the drive, you value what goes into it.</p></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Skip the Guesswork. Keep the Quality</h3><p class="text-[20px] text-[#cecece] leading-[34px] mb-3">Brand-new parts are costly and often unnecessary. Our OEM parts provide factory fitment, long-lasting reliability, and serious savings. Request a quote in seconds — no login, no calls, just answers. You’ll love the price. And trust the part.</p></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Buick Models We Support</h3><p class="text-[20px] text-[#cecece] leading-[34px] mb-3">From legacy sedans to new-gen SUVs, we stock parts for a wide range of Buick models. Need rare or older parts? Our salvage network helps track down even the most elusive used Buick parts online.</p><ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-1 text-[#cecece]"><li>Buick Enclave</li><li>Buick Encore</li><li>Buick Encore GX</li><li>Buick Regal</li><li>Buick LaCrosse</li><li>Buick Lucerne</li><li>Buick LeSabre</li><li>Buick Century</li><li>Buick Park Avenue</li><li>Buick Verano</li><li>Buick Roadmaster</li><li>Buick Riviera</li><li>Buick Skylark</li><li>Buick Wildcat</li></ul></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Why Buick Owners Choose PartsCentral</h3><ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2 text-[#cecece]"><li>Rigorous quality inspections</li><li>Nationwide shipping</li><li>Competitive pricing</li><li>Secure checkout and easy returns</li><li>Customer support available 7 days a week</li></ul></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Bring Your Buick Back in Just a Few Clicks</h3><p class="text-[20px] text-[#cecece] leading-[34px] mb-3">Your Buick was built to last. We’re here to make sure it does. Search by model or VIN, get your quote, and order your used Buick parts with confidence. Thousands of Buick owners trust PartsCentral — join them today and keep driving on your terms.</p><p class="mt-4 font-bold text-white">Request a quote and order today.</p></div></div><div class="w-full mt-20 py-16 sm:py-20 px-4 sm:px-8  bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/20 text-center rounded-2xl"><h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Find Quality <!-- -->Used Buick Parts for Sale<!-- --> Parts Today?</h2><p class="text-white/80 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8 text-sm sm:text-base">Get fast pricing, expert guidance, and nationwide delivery on quality used auto parts for your <!-- -->Used Buick Parts for Sale<!-- -->.</p><a href="/" class="inline-block  bg-[#00A3FF]  text-white px-7 sm:px-9 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(0,163,255,0.45)] hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(0,163,255,0.7)] transition-all duration-300 hover:opacity-95">Find My Parts</a></div></section><section class="w-full flex flex-col items-center px-6 py-16 bg-[#07142B] text-[#E8F3FF]"><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold font-orbitron mb-10 text-center">USED <!-- -->BUICK<!-- --> AUTO PARTS</h2><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 max-w-7xl mx-auto"><ul class="space-y-2 text-lg leading-7 font-jaldi list-disc list-inside text-[#cecece]"><li>Buick<!-- --> <!-- -->Engine Assembly</li><li>Buick<!-- --> <!-- -->Transmission</li><li>